# 🗄️ MSSQL Server to Azure SQL — End-to-End ETL Pipeline

A production-ready **End-to-End Data Engineering Pipeline** built with
**Azure Data Factory** that extracts data from **On-Premises SQL Server**,
transforms it through **Medallion Architecture** layers, and loads it
into **Azure SQL Database**.

