## 📌 Pipeline 2 — Silver_DataFlow_Gold (ADF Mapping Data Flow)

**Pipeline:** `Silver_DataFlow_Gold`
**Data Flow Status:** ✅ Success
**Cluster Startup Time:** 1s 379ms
**Number of Transformations:** 5

### 🔁 Data Flow Steps
### ⚙️ Transformation Details

| Step              | Type            | Purpose                                      |
|-------------------|-----------------|----------------------------------------------|
| `ADLSSilverGold`  | Source          | Read data from ADLS Gen2 Silver Layer        |
| `EditDates`       | Derived Column  | Standardize date formats for analytics       |
| `PurchaseColumn`  | Derived Column  | Apply business rules on purchase columns     |
| `select1`         | Select          | Filter & select required columns only        |
| `sinkADLSGold`    | Sink            | Load clean data to ADLS Gen2 Gold Layer      |

