## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Azure Data Factory** — Pipeline orchestration & monitoring
- **SQL Server (On-Premises)** — Relational source database
- **Self-Hosted Integration Runtime** — On-Prem to Cloud connectivity
- **Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2** — Silver & Gold layer storage
- **ADF Mapping Data Flow** — Visual ETL transformation engine
- **Azure SQL Database** — Final Gold layer destination
- **Azure Copy Activity** — Efficient data movement
- **Medallion Architecture** — Bronze → Silver → Gold pattern

---

## 📊 What This Demonstrates

- ✅ **On-Premises to Cloud** data migration using Self-Hosted IR
- ✅ **Medallion Architecture** (Silver → Gold)
- ✅ **ADF Mapping Data Flow** with 5 transformations
- ✅ **Date formatting & column selection** logic
- ✅ **Business rule application** on purchase columns
- ✅ Real-world **pipeline execution metrics**
- ✅ Zero data loss — 100 rows in = 100 rows out
- ✅ Fast cluster startup — **1s 379ms** ⚡

---

## 🔑 Key Highlight — Self-Hosted Integration Runtime
> Self-Hosted IR installed on local machine enables
> secure data movement from On-Premises SQL Server
> to Azure Cloud without exposing the database publicly.

